        information provided in this manual might then not be accurate.
      </para>

      <para>The Git repository is located at:</para>

      <programlisting>
http://github.com/ironjacamar/ironjacamar
      </programlisting>

      <para>You can find additional information about this in the developer guide.</para>

   </section>
